<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l14">bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> . wenn das <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> ſo er anheim ſey on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l15">als wır das <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt auch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>VV<ex>er</ex>e</expan> </ab>
