<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l21">was er 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jm </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_208_r1l20">ewch </ab></add> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſchuldıg ſey ʒutun . getrawn wır eẅch wol Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l22">lat eẅch des von dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l23">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
