</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="104r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Erking<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Sawnsheim zum Stepfanssberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Erking<ex>er,</ex></expan> als ir uns aber
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> des <expan>Hübn<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und der
                        wollen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>Hans<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Hübn<ex>er</ex></expan> für uns besant und
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu rede gesaczt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Der hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> als auch vor, daz er von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> wollen niht gewest hab zu den
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en,</ex></expan> do im woll geschikt wurd; im hab
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, der <expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>, etwievil
                        wollen geschikt an der schult, die er im schuldig sey, als er vormals andre
                        jar auch getan hab. Dewcht ewch <expan>ab<ex>er,</ex></expan> daz ir
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu im icht zu
                                <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, so well er
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn das
                            <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, so er anheim sey on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, als wir das
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst auch
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er,</ex></expan> daz ir daran niht <add>ein</add>
<expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> on red niht <expan>gelass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        möcht, so spricht <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, so well er <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        für den <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>lantfr<ex>id</ex></expan>
<add>mit ewch</add>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und da nach spruch und antwurt
                                <expan>erkenne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en,</ex></expan> was er <add>ewch</add>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> schuldig sey zu tun. Getrawn wir ewch wol, ir
                        lat ewch des von dem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan>; denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
